LEGACY CLINICS - QMS DOCKER DEPLOYMENT CONFIG 
Version: 1.2
Owner: Valery
Backend: /backend/main.py  (FastAPI + Socket.IO)
Frontend: /frontend/dist   (built Vite output)
DB: Postgres container (recommended)
Reverse Proxy: Nginx container serves frontend + proxies /api + /socket.io

============================================================
1) REQUIRED FILES TO ADD (VERY IMPORTANT)
============================================================
A) Make backend a python package:
- Ensure this exists:
  backend/__init__.py

If missing:
