B) Add health endpoint (recommended) in backend/main.py:
  @app.get("/health")
  def health():
      return {"status": "ok"}

C) Make SECRET_KEY come from env (important):
Change:
  SECRET_KEY = "supersecretkey_change_me_in_production"
To:
  SECRET_KEY = os.getenv("SECRET_KEY", "dev_only_change_me")

