8) IMPORTANT: FRONTEND API BASE URL
============================================================
Because Nginx uses /api/ prefix, your frontend should call:
  /api/login
  /api/queue
  /api/stats
etc.

If your frontend currently calls http://HOST:8000 directly,
change it to relative "/api".

============================================================
9) COMMON ERRORS + FIXES
============================================================
- "attempted relative import with no known parent package"
  Fix:
    * ensure backend/__init__.py exists
    * run uvicorn backend.main:socket_app (not main:app)
    * ensure PYTHONPATH=/app

- Socket.IO not connecting
  Fix:
    * run socket_app, not app
    * nginx location /socket.io/ has Upgrade/Connection headers

- Static/templates missing
  Fix:
    * ensure COPY backend /app/backend
    * ensure paths in code are correct
      (If needed, set StaticFiles(directory="/app/backend/static"))

